quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,73,ae paighambar! kafiroon aur munhafiqon se laro. aur un par sakhti karo. aur un ka thikana دورخ hai aur woh buri jagah hai
  9,74,yeh khuda ki kasmain khatay hain ke unhon ne ( to kuch ) nahi kaha halaank unhon ne kufar ka kalma kaha hai aur yeh islam laane ke baad kafir hogaye hain aur aisi baat ka qasad kar chukay hain jis par qudrat nahi paske. aur unhon ne ( musalmanoon mein ) aib hi kon sa dekha hai siwa is ke ke khuda ne apne fazl se aur is ke paighambar ne ( apni meharbani se ) un ko doulat mand kar diya hai. to agar yeh log tauba karlen to un ke haq mein behtar hoga. aur agar munh phair len to un ko duniya aur akhirat mein dukh dainay wala azaab day ga aur zameen mein un ka koi dost aur madadgaar nah hoga
  9,75,aur un mein se baaz aisay hain jinhon ne khuda se ehadkiya tha ke agar woh hum ko apni meharbani se ( maal ) ataa farmaiye ga to hum zaroor khairaatkiya karen ge aur naik karon mein ho jayen ge
  9,76,lekin jab khuda ne un ko apne fazl se ( maal ) diya to is mein bukhal karne lagey aur ( apne ehad se ) rogrdani karkay phir baithy
  9,77,to khuda ne is ka injaam yehkiya ke is roz taq ke liye jis mein woh khuda ke rubaroo haazir hon ge un ke dilon mein nifaq daal diya is liye ke unhon ne khuda se jo wadakiya tha is ke khilaafkiya aur is liye ke woh jhoot boltay they
  9,78,kiya un ko maloom nahi ke khuda un ke bheidoon aur mashwaron taq se waaqif hai aur yeh ke woh ghaib ki baatein jan-nay wala hai
  9,79,jo ( Zee istetat ) musalman dil khol kar khairaat karte hain aur jo ( be chaaray ghareeb sirf itna hi kama satke hain jitni mazdoori karte ( aur thori si kamaai mein se kharch bhi karte ) hain un par jo ( munhafiq ) ta'an karte hain aur hanstay hain. khuda un par hanstaa hai aur un ke liye takleef dainay wala azaab ( tayyar ) hai
